ealize……\n[02:55.240]Hook:\n[02:57.759]I see nobody but U\n[03:00.699]I called it something right\n[03:03.000]I feel nobody but U\n[03:05.819]Around the coastline and we run\n[03:08.330]I see nobody but U\n[03:11.139]I called it something wrong\n[03:13.509]I feel nobody but U but U but U\n[03:18.729]I see nobody but U\n[03:27.030]I called it something right\n[03:29.379]I see nobody but U\n[03:32.250]I called it something wrong\n[03:34.560]I feel nobody but U but U but U\n[03:41.930]监制：李俊驹\n[03:43.180]出品人：李宏杰\n[03:44.020]出品公司：WR/OC Records（北京惟又双文化传播有限公司）\n', 'http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1459232593.mp3', 'http://p2.music.126.net/li19i75jz6GGOT79IyAjYA==/109951165100592039.jpg?param=300x300');
